title: Grateful Dead Live at Boston Garden on 1993-09-30
description:
Set 1

Here Comes Sunshine, Spoonful, Candyman, El Paso*, Broken Arrow, Stagger Lee, Easy Answers-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Lucy In The Sky With Diamonds, Wave To The Wind-> Crazy Fingers-> Estimated Prophet-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Space-> The Other One-> Wharf Rat-> Not Fade Away, E: Brokedown Palace

* Weir on acoustic
